Map showing all restaurats across US

food %>% leaflet() %>% addProviderTiles("Esri") %>% 
    addMarkers(~longitude, ~latitude,
               clusterOptions = markerClusterOptions(),
               label = ~name,
               popup = paste0(
                   "<b> Name: </b>",
                   food$name,
                   "<br>",
                   "<b> Categories: </b>",
                   food$categories,
                   "<br>",
                   "<b> Address: </b>",
                   food$address)) %>% 
  setView(lng = median(food$longitude),
          lat = median(food$latitude),
          zoom = 3)

Filter applied to show only Wendys restaurant accross US

wendy <- unique(food$name)[grepl("Wendy's",unique(food$name))]
wendy
## [1] "Wendy's"                    "Wendy's Valenti Management"
wendy <- wendy[-2]
wendy
## [1] "Wendy's"
food %>% subset(name %in% wendy) -> only_wendy_data

only_wendy_data %>%
    leaflet() %>% addProviderTiles("Esri") %>% addMarkers(~longitude, ~latitude,
                                                                clusterOptions = markerClusterOptions(),
                                                                label = ~name,
                                                                popup = paste0(
                                                                "<b> Name: </b>",
                                                                only_wendy_data$name,
                                                                "<br>",
                                                                "<b> Categories: </b>",
                                                                only_wendy_data$categories,
                                                                "<br>",
                                                                "<b> Address: </b>",
                                                                only_wendy_data$address)) %>% 
  setView(lng = median(only_wendy_data$longitude),
          lat = median(only_wendy_data$latitude),
          zoom = 3)
